        <mxCell id="S89zjXSp-3V75uFwfCcD-21" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;problems with foreign direct investments.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;More focus on capital intensive industries&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - which leads to employment of relatively less number of workers. in labour abundant&amp;nbsp; country creates poverty and unemployment.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.&amp;nbsp; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Regional disparity&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;: FDI likely flows towards regions well&amp;nbsp; endowed with natural resources and infrastructure.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Outflow of foreign exchange&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; technology brought in with FDI requires imported raw material also a lot of money is to be paid in foreign exchange on account of Interest \ dividend&amp;nbsp; payments. Such outflows of foreign exchange puts a strain on the balance of payments.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.&amp;nbsp; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Undercutting domestic producers&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;. FDI firms adopt anti competitive practices to wipe out domestic suppliers&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.&amp;nbsp; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Exploitation of natural resources&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dual economy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - dual economy with a developed foreign sector and an underdeveloped domestic sector.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7.&amp;nbsp; &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dilution of environmental standards&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - continuance to lower labour or environmental standards in host countries.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-85" y="1590" width="370" height="370" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S89zjXSp-3V75uFwfCcD-27" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;curved=1;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="S89zjXSp-3V75uFwfCcD-25" target="S89zjXSp-3V75uFwfCcD-1">
